+ * Rudimentary ISO 10646/Unicode/UTF-8 character set support by
+ * Markus Kuhn, <mskuhn@immd4.informatik.uni-erlangen.de>.
+ *
+ * Dynamic allocation of consoles, aeb@cwi.nl, May 1994
